a}} ''Srí Lanka'' |- | [[Sinhala language|Sinhala]] - [[Tamil language|Tamil]] | [[Sri Jayawardenapura-Kotte]] | Srí Jajevardenepúra |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Sudan}} ''Súdan'' |- | [[Arabic language|Arabic]] - [[English language|English]] | [[Khartoum|Kharṭūm]] - [[Khartoum]] | Kartúm |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Suriname}} ''Súrínam'' |- | [[Dutch language|Dutch]] | [[Paramaribo]] | Paramaríbó |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Sweden}} ''Svíþjóð'' |- | rowspan=6 valign=top | [[Swedish language|Swedish]] | [[Gothenburg|Göteborg]] | Gautaborg |- | [[Helsingborg]] | Helsingjaborg |- | [[Lund]] | Lundur |- | [[Malmö]] | Málmhaugar |- | [[Stockholm]] | Stokkhólmur |- | [[Uppsala]] | Uppsalir |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Switzerland}} ''Sviss'' |- | [[German language|German]] - [[French language|French]] | [[Basel]] - [[Bâle]] | Boslaraborg (obsolete) |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Syria}} ''Sýrland'' |- | [[Arabic language|Arabic]] | [[Damascus|Dimašq]] | Damaskus |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Tajikistan}} ''Tadsjikistan'' |- | [[Tajik language|Tajik]] | [[Dushanbe]] | Dúshanbe |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Tanzania}} ''Tansanía'' |- | [[Swahili language|Swahili]] | [[Dodoma]] | Dódóma |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Thailand}} ''Taíland'' |- | [[Thai language|Thai]] | [[Bangkok|Krung Thep]] | Bangkok |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Tonga}} ''Tonga'' |- | [[Tongan language|Tongan]] - [[English language|English]] | [[Nukuʻalofa]] | Núkúalófa |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Turkey}} ''Tyrkland'' |- | [[Turkish language|Turkish]] | [[İstanbul]] | Mikligarður (historical), Istanbúl (current) |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Ukraine}} ''Úkraína'' |- | [[Ukrainian language|Ukrainian]] | [[Kiev]] | Kænugarður |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|United Arab Emirates}} ''Sameinuðu arabísku furstadæmin'' |- | rowspan=3 valign=top | [[Arabic language|Arabic]] | [[Abu Dhabi|Abū Zabī]] | Abú Dabí |- | [[Ajman|'Ajmān]] | Adsman |- | [[Dubai|Dubayy]] | Dúbæ |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|United Kingdom}} ''Bretland'' |- | rowspan=12 valign=top | [[English language|English]] | [[Aberdeen]] | Apardjón (obsolete) |- | [[Canterbury]] | Kantaraborg |- | [[Dover]] | Dofrar (little used) |- | [[Edinburgh]] | Edinborg |- | [[Great Yarmouth|Yarmouth]] | Járnamóða (little used) |- | [[Cambridge]] | Kambabryggja (little used) |- | [[Lerwick]] | Leirvík |- | [[London]] | Lundúnir |- | [[Southampton]] | Suðurhamtún (little used) |- | [[Oxford]] | Öxnafurða (little used) |- | [[Scarborough, North Yorkshire|Scarborough]] | Skarðaborg (obsolete) |- | [[York]] | Jórvík |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|United States}} ''Bandaríkin'' |- | rowspan=3 valign=top | [[English language|English]] | [[California]] | Kalifornía |- | [[New York City|New York]] | Nýja-Jórvík (not in common use, a jocular term of academic pretension) |- | [[South Dakota]] | Suður-Dakóta |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Uruguay}} ''Úrúgvæ'' |- | [[Spanish language|Spanish]] | [[Montevideo]] | Montevídeó |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Uzbekistan}} ''Úsbekistan'' |- | [[Uzbek language|Uzbek]] | [[Tashkent|Toshkent]] | Taskent |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Vatican City}} ''Vatíkanið'' or ''Páfagarður'' |- | [[Latin]] | [[Status Civitatis Vaticanae]] | Páfagarður |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Venezuela}} ''Venesúela'' |- | [[Spanish language|Spanish]] | [[Caracas]] | Karakas |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Vietnam}} ''Víetnam'' |- | rowspan=2 valign=top | [[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]] | [[Hanoi|Hà Nội]] | Hanoí |- | [[Ho Chi Minh City|Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh]] | Hochimin-borg |- ! colspan=3 style="text-align:left;" | {{flagu|Zambia}} ''Sambía''